revenue-driven sales culture with aggressive yet achievable sales goals Create and execute innovative sales processes, techniques and campaigns to cultivate the sales funnel; nurture and develop leads by leveraging a variety of sales touches and meetings Collaborate with leadership to drive outcome-based solutions into new business opportunities; provide strategic guidance on sales strategies and methodologies, proposal building and closing process to support growth and revenue goals Establish KPIs and methods of measurement to analyze sales activities and performance, adjusting strategies as needed Forecast accurate sales information and maintain system of record to facilitate effective planning and execution of sales strategies as well as effective decision-making Apply proactive measures to assess health of client relationship and understand how/when to engage; strengthen existing relationships by mentoring and guiding account management team in exceeding client needs and expectations Maintain and share market trends and competitive intelligence regarding products, services and pricing; make recommendations on opportunities to pursue and how to prioritize and leverage resources for delivery Partner with leaders to maintain a high retention rate, ensure on-time renewals and create expansion opportunities to cross-sell, up-sell and add incremental services Act as liaison between clients and organization by providing feedback in an effort to manage relationships, improve services and retain clients Develop and manage the annual sales and marketing budget TEAMS, TOOLS &TALENT Develop a team of high-performing sales members by coaching and inspiring, providing on-going and timely feedback for learning and development; create a culture that inspires and encourages successful sales behaviors and competency Provide coaching and mentoring to sales team members; ensure sufficient resources and tools are readily available and accessible to team members Establish and communicate aggressive yet achievable sales goals to team members and support team by providing progress updates; redirect sales strategies as appropriate MARKETING Collaborate with leadership to align sales and marketing strategies to drive business development and sales pipelining efforts Partner with internal team to review sales and marketing collateral ensuring materials are brand relevant; offer input regarding updates to keep materials fresh, timely and engaging Expand and evolve existing social media presence by sharing and promoting company information, events and other relevant information through blogs, etc. THE QUALIFICATIONS Proven experience as a \u201chunter\u201d building business development and a pipeline of sales leads remotely, even in an ambiguous and uncertain economic climate Proven success creating and implementing an energetic sales culture including a strong sales philosophy, methodology and mindset Demonstrated success in consistently building and mentoring remote sales team members in achieving aggressive yet attainable sales goals on a quarterly and annual basis Expertise in conducting and applying competitive intelligence, applying as appropriate Strong leadership presence with the ability to build relationships, engaging and influencing clients and C-Suite executives, promoting solutions to complex business problems and situations Knowledge of and experience in contributing to the development of sales and marketing tools and collateral via print, digital and social channels Excellent communication skills both verbal and written with the ability to create and deliver impactful presentations that engage and influence others Bachelor\u2019s degree preferred but not required 8-10 years of experience creating and driving sales strategies that meet financial goals; marketing knowledge preferred If this job interests you but you aren\u2019t certain if you meet all of theÂ requirements, apply anyway! More Jobs Website Twitter Or view all jobs: Develo